Lung X-Ray Image Dataset Overview:
The dataset was published in “Mendeley data” website.

The dataset supports the detection and classification of lung diseases through high-quality X-ray images from hospitals, clinics, and healthcare institutions.

Total Images: 3,475
Classes:
Normal: 1,250 images (healthy lungs).
Lung Opacity: 1,125 images (varied abnormalities).
Viral Pneumonia: 1,100 images (viral infections).

Dataset link: https://data.mendeley.com/datasets/9d55cttn5h/1
